  (sp + signExtend12 3976 ↦ₘ jOld) ** (sp + signExtend12 3984 ↦ₘ (2 : Word)) **
  ((sp + 32) ↦ₘ v0) ** ((sp + signExtend12 4056) ↦ₘ u0) **
