    loopBodyN2CallSkipJ0PostV4NoX1 sp base v0 v1 v2 v3 u0 u1 u2 u3 uTop scratchMem =
      loopBodyN2CallSkipPostJScratchNoX1 sp base (0 : Word)
        (divKTrialCallV4QHat u2 u1 v1)
